---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Breath Studio Privacy Policy | Pondering Silver"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Breath Studio mobile application."
>
  <article class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-8 text-gray-700">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><strong>Effective Date: May 25, 2026</strong></p>
      <p>
        Pondering Silver (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;us,&quot; or &quot;our&quot;) operates the Breath Studio mobile
        application (the &quot;Service&quot;).
      </p>
      <p>
        This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal
        data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Information Collection and Use</h2>
      <p>
        We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) from you. You are not required
        to create an account or provide an email address, name, or phone number to use Breath Studio.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Stored Locally</h3>
      <p>
        Breath Studio stores your breathing routines, custom practices, and app preferences locally on
        your device. This data is managed using Android&apos;s DataStore system.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Backups</h3>
      <p>
        If you have enabled &quot;Back up my data&quot; on your Android device, the local data stored by
        Breath Studio may be automatically backed up to your Google Drive by the Android operating
        system. This data is not accessible by Pondering Silver.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2. Log Data (Diagnostics)</h2>
      <p>
        Our Service includes a local diagnostic log that records system information and application
        events (such as device model, Android version, and app-specific actions). This information is
        used for troubleshooting and is stored only in the temporary memory of your device. It is not
        automatically transmitted to our servers or any third parties.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">3. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Retention</h3>
      <p>
        Because Breath Studio stores all your data (such as custom breathing routines and app settings) locally on your device, we retain this data for as long as the application is installed on your device. We do not host, store, or transmit your data on our own servers.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Deletion</h3>
      <p>
        You have complete control over your data and can delete it at any time:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
        <li>
          <strong>Clearing App Data:</strong> You can delete all locally stored routines and settings by going to your device's <em>Settings &gt; Apps &gt; Breath Studio &gt; Storage</em> and selecting <strong>Clear Data</strong> or <strong>Clear Storage</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Uninstalling the App:</strong> Uninstalling Breath Studio from your device will automatically delete all data and preferences associated with the application.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Backups:</strong> If you have enabled Android's automatic backup system, your app settings may be backed up to your Google Drive. You can delete or manage these backups at any time through your Google Drive storage settings or your device's system backup settings (typically found under <em>Settings &gt; Google &gt; Backup</em>).
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">4. Service Providers</h2>
      <p>
        We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our Service (&quot;Service
        Providers&quot;), to provide the Service on our behalf, or to perform Service-related services.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Google Play Services</h3>
      <p>
        Breath Studio uses Google Play Services for application delivery and core functionality. Google
        may collect information as described in their
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">In-App Billing</h3>
      <p>
        We use Google Play Billing for optional support and donations. All payment information is
        processed securely by Google. We do not collect or store your credit card numbers or other
        financial information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are files with a small amount of data that are commonly used as anonymous unique
        identifiers. Breath Studio does not use cookies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">6. Links to Other Sites</h2>
      <p>
        Our Service contains links to other sites (such as https://ponderingsilver.com). If you click on
        a third-party link, you will be directed to that site. Note that these external sites are not
        operated by us. Therefore, we strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of these websites.
        We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or
        practices of any third-party sites or services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">7. Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our Services do not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally
        identifiable information from children under 13.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page
        periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy
        on this page.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Website:</strong>
        <a href="https://ponderingsilver.com">https://ponderingsilver.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
